      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONNER'S RAIN (8) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage third, beaten one length (17.25) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6 over 300m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Capable of going well again. CATCH MY DESIGN (5) is rarely out of the finish, recording 10 places from 21 starts. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (19.80) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading player again. RAVEN ZAYLEE (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (20.26) last time in a TG1-4W at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to run well. SPRINGVALE MARGI (1) can fill a top-three spot.",
